## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="50c52-179"><xref:System.Data.ParameterDirection> が出力され、関連付けられた <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleCommand> の実行が値を返さない場合、<xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleParameter> には null 値が含まれます。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="50c52-179">If the <xref:System.Data.ParameterDirection> is output, and execution of the associated <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleCommand> does not return a value, the <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleParameter> contains a null value.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="50c52-180"><xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleCommand.ExecuteReader%2A> を呼び出すことによって返される `Output`、`InputOut`、および `ReturnValue` パラメーターには、<xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataReader.Close%2A> で <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataReader>を呼び出すまでアクセスできません。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="50c52-180">`Output`, `InputOut`, and `ReturnValue` parameters returned by calling <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleCommand.ExecuteReader%2A> cannot be accessed until you call <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataReader.Close%2A> on the <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataReader>.</span></span>  
  
   
  
## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="50c52-181">次の例では、<xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleParameter> を作成し、そのプロパティの一部を設定します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="50c52-181">The following example creates a <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleParameter> and sets some of its properties.</span></span>  
  
```vb  
Public Sub CreateOracleDbParameter()  
   Dim parameter As New OracleParameter()  
   parameter.ParameterName = "pDName"  
   parameter.DbType = DbType.String  
   parameter.Value = "ENGINEERING"  
   parameter.SourceColumn = "DName"  
End Sub  
```  
  
```csharp  
public void CreateOracleDbParameter()   
{  
   OracleParameter parameter = new OracleParameter();  
   parameter.ParameterName = "pDName";  
   parameter.DbType = DbType.String;  
   parameter.Value = "ENGINEERING";  
   parameter.SourceColumn = "DName";  
}  
```

  
  
## Remarks  
